ActCanadian Commercial Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of MARIE-LUCIE MORIN of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Canadian Commercial Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Gero, who has resigned.
